<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .main-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
            
        }

        .row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .box {
            flex: 1; /* Equal width for each box */
            max-width:300px;
            border:1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

            .box:hover {
                transform: scale(1.05);
            }

            .box h2 {
                color: #333;
            }

            .box p {
                color: #666;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    
    <div class="main-container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="box">
                <h2>Lost Pet Reporting</h2>
                <p>Report missing pets and aid in a quicker reunion.</p>
                <a href="/LOSTPETREPORTING/LPRHome" class="button-link">Go to Lost Pet Reporting</a>
            </div>

            <div class="box">
                <h2>Pet Memorial</h2>
                <p>Celebrate the joy your pet brought into your life.</p>
                <a href="/PETMEMORIAL/PMHome" class="button-link">Go to Pet Memorial</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="box">
                <h2>Coping Resources</h2>
                <p>Discover tools to navigate the emotional journey of losing a pet.</p>
                <a href="/COPINGRESOURCES/CRHome" class="button-link">Go to Coping Resources</a>
            </div>

            <div class="box">
                <h2>Settings</h2>
                <p>Customise your account settings or reach out to us</p>
                <a href="/SETTINGS/Settings" class="button-link">Go to Settings</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
